I don't know how to use Jeppview with Jeppesen Mobile TC but I make Pdf's from all the Jeppview plates with eDocPrinter Pdf Pro. This program is able to recognise the italic identifier of each airport and full automatic produces Pdf plates with bookmarks of each airport. To make a Pdf of the Netherlands for instance takes only 2 minutes. Germany 10 minutes. With the bookmark feature in Goodreader for the Ipad you can find each airport in a split second and have all the plates of that airport available. Before transfer the Jeppview plates to Pdf's it is important to correctly define the identifier. This is Arial 20pt italic. I use my Ipad as a backup with my flighttraining and it works smoothly. Have fun.
